<task id="task_add_beans">
    <title>Add coffee beans to the grinder</title>
    <shortdesc><abbreviated-form keyref="coffeebean"/> are simply added to the grinder by lifting
        the grinder cover and pouring in the beans. The coffee grinder <ph keyref="product-name-A"/>
        must be at least 10% full to work properly. Add <term keyref="coffeebean">coffee
            beans</term> to the <ph keyref="product-name"/> grinder every morning.</shortdesc>
